metadata.name: Drama
metadata.description:
Take the dreary night and the sunset that flooded it. Through the dark silhouettes of living oaks and dying pines, He is barely visible. He is intensely drawn to the drama. More precisely, he fell in love with being in it. She gives him strength, nourishes and leads him forward through the black water.

Word. Should it only mean what it means? If so, then there is also a draw in chess. But rarely. Less often than a victory for one of the sides.
